Maharashtra
Oct 31, 2014
Murder
Description:
			The police has arrested a man for killing his infant daughter after her body was found in a well in Borta village Murtizapur taluka of Akola district.

Allegedly, a villager, Kailash Bandhot (40) strangulated his his one-year infant daughter to death on Thursday, after his wife failed to deliver a male child a month ago, the police said.

He has two daughters and wanted a son.

